import React from 'react'
import { Container , Nav , Navbar , NavDropdown} from 'react-bootstrap'

const Menu = () => {
  return (
    <Navbar bg="light" className='shadow' expand="false">
        <Container>
            <Navbar.Brand href="#home">Trouver Logo</Navbar.Brand>
            <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="basic-navbar-nav" />
            <Navbar.Collapse id="basic-navbar-nav">
                <Nav className="me-auto">
                    <Nav.Link href="#home">Home</Nav.Link>
                    <Nav.Link href="#link">BI - Dashboard</Nav.Link>
                    <NavDropdown title="FormulÃ¡rios de Atesto" id="basic-nav-dropdown">
                        <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.1">Form1</NavDropdown.Item>
                        <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.2"></NavDropdown.Item>
                        <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.3">Something</NavDropdown.Item>
                        <NavDropdown.Item href="#action/3.4">
                            Separated link
                        </NavDropdown.Item>
                    </NavDropdown>
                </Nav>
            </Navbar.Collapse>
        </Container>
    </Navbar>

  )
}

export default Menu
